{
  "texts": [
    "In the final stage, the output feature maps from both attention processes are concatenated.",
    "These regions of interest are amplified in the fused feature map, while redundant features are discarded.",
    "To collect the most accurate target data while reducing unnecessary data, the target regions are weighted (distributed).",
    "Soft attention [5], which is differentiable and permits end-to-end training of CNN models.",
    "Most soft attention models use attention templates to locate unique aspects that align weights for discrete sequences or image segments."
  ]
}